flowchart TD
  U[User (Browser / Frontend)]
  UI[Web UI (templates + static JS/CSS)]
  F[Flask Server\n(routes.py)]
  Upload[/POST /api/upload-dataset/]
  Train[/POST /api/train/]
  Predict[/POST /predict/]
  Stats[/GET /api/stats & /api/model-evaluation]
  Preproc[Preprocessing\n(preprocess_text / preprocess_for_display)]
  ML[SentimentModel\n(TF-IDF -> ComplementNB)]
  Seed[CSV parsing & rating->label\n(map_rating_to_sentiment)]
  DB[(Database)\nTrainingData, PredictionHistory, TrainingLog]
  ModelFiles[(Model files)\nnaive_bayes_model.pkl\ntfidf_vectorizer.pkl, metrics.pkl]

  U -->|interact / klik / upload| UI
  UI -->|HTTP requests| F

  %% Upload dataset
  F --> Upload
  Upload -->|read CSV| Seed
  Seed -->|map rating -> label, parse tanggal| DB
  Upload -->|clear old training data| DB
  Upload -->|delete model files -> set model not trained| ModelFiles
  Upload -->|log upload| DB

  %% Train
  F --> Train
  Train -->|load training rows| DB
  Train -->|preprocess each text| Preproc
  Preproc --> ML
  ML -->|vectorizer.fit + model.fit (oversampling)| ModelFiles
  ML -->|predict_batch -> nb_predicted_label| DB
  Train -->|log training| DB

  %% Single predict
  F --> Predict
  Predict -->|preprocess_for_display| Preproc
  Preproc --> ML
  ML -->|vectorize.transform + predict| F
  F -->|save PredictionHistory| DB

  %% Dashboard / Stats
  F --> Stats
  Stats -->|read training & prediction data| DB
  Stats -->|use nb_predicted_label untuk analisis| ML
